casebody.data:
No. 271,

Misc.

Ferro v. Wilson, Warden, et al. Petitioner pro se. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, Arlo E. Smith, Chief Assistant Attorney General, and Edward P. O’Brien, Deputy Attorney General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
